title: Episode 6: Place Matters
itunes:author: Jonathan Rodden and Margaret Weir
description: Contributor(s): Jonathan Rodden and Margaret Weir | Does where we reside influence how we vote or even how much it costs to live ? Or is it the other way around? This episode, we take a look at the role geography plays in politics, inequality, and more.
